        "subject": "feat(ui): show PR merge time on live card active badge (#1343)",
        "body": "Display the PR merge time on the Active section's PR badge in the live\n(non-history) card view, consistent with the existing history view.\n\nFalls back to environment.pullRequest when history[0].pullRequest has no\nid (e.g. externally or manually merged PRs), treating both state=merged\nand externallyMergedOrClosed=true as displayable.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jonathan Winters <wintersjonathan0@gmail.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
